    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "The stable build for 0.12 appears to have failed with transient network errors.\n\n#### build:\nhttps://launchpad.net/~neovim-snap/neovim-ppa/+snap/nvim-stable/+build/3107596\n\n#### amd64 log:\nhttps://launchpadlibrarian.net/854635787/buildlog_snap_ubuntu_jammy_amd64_nvim-stable_BUILDING.txt.gz\n\nThe failure extracted from the above.\n```\n...\nerror: cannot perform the following tasks:\n- Download snap \"snapd\" (26382) from channel \"stable\" (Get \"https://storage.snapcraftcontent.com/download-origin/local/PMrrV4ml8uWuEUDBT8dSGnKUYbevVhc4_26382.snap?interactive=1&sig=IlBNcnJWNG1sOHVXdUVVREJUOGRTR25LVVliZXZWaGM0XzI2MzgyLnNuYXAi.HK6aQA.EP1Ip_daITdztlwAkalQFp-4mkk\": net/http: timeout awaiting response headers)\nInstall failed\nTraceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"/usr/lib/python3/dist-packages/lpbuildd/target/build_snap.py\", line 319, in run\n    self.install()\n  File \"/usr/lib/python3/dist-packages/lpbuildd/target/build_snap.py\", line 181, in install\n    self.backend.run(\n  File \"/usr/lib/python3/dist-packages/lpbuildd/target/lxd.py\", line 735, in run\n    subprocess.check_call(cmd, **kwargs)\n  File \"/usr/lib/python3.12/subprocess.py\", line 413, in check_call\n    raise CalledProcessError(retcode, cmd)\nsubprocess.CalledProcessError: Command '['lxc', 'exec', 'lp-jammy-amd64', '--', 'linux64', 'snap', 'install', '--classic', '--channel=stable/launchpad-buildd', 'snapcraft']' returned non-zero exit status 1.\n...\n```",
